>>course: dinner
>>vegan: true
>>time: 80

Heat the #oven{} to 220°C / 200°C fan / gas 7.

Rub @olive oil{} and @salt{} over @large baking potatoes{} and put directly on the top shelf of the oven. Bake for ~{20%minutes}.

Turn down the oven to 190C/170C fan/gas 5 and bake for ~{45%minutes} up to an hour, until the skin is crisp and the flesh soft.

Cut a cross on top of each potato, squeeze the sides, add the soured cream and your favourite toppings.
